sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Entrypoint as CLI or Lambda
    participant Config
    participant Crawler
    participant RegistryAPI as Registry API
    participant Storage
    participant Notifier
    participant External

    User->>Entrypoint: Start execution
    Entrypoint->>Config: Load configuration
    Config-->>Entrypoint: CrawlerConfig

    loop For each registry
        Entrypoint->>Crawler: Initialize crawler (ECR/DockerHub/Quay)
        Crawler->>Crawler: Build HTTP session with retry

        loop For each search term
            Crawler->>RegistryAPI: Search for term
            RegistryAPI-->>Crawler: Results (paginated)
            Crawler->>Crawler: Apply filter pattern (regex)
            Crawler->>Crawler: Exclude company-owned repos
            Crawler->>Crawler: Deduplicate results
            Crawler-->>Entrypoint: List of ImageResult
        end
    end

    loop For each ImageResult
        Entrypoint->>Storage: exists(image)?
        Storage->>Storage: Query DynamoDB
        Storage-->>Entrypoint: True / False

        alt Image is new
            Entrypoint->>Storage: save(image)
            Storage->>External: Write to DynamoDB

            loop For each notifier
                Entrypoint->>Notifier: notify(image)
                Notifier->>External: Send notification (Slack/Webhook)
                Notifier-->>Entrypoint: Success / Failure
            end
        else Image exists
            Entrypoint->>Entrypoint: Skip (already tracked)
        end
    end

    Entrypoint-->>User: Return count of new images
